 but to fold.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"Kadeena Coxhas\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"the past decade\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"the hand\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 457}, {\"ngram\": \"her body\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 471}, {\"ngram\": \"no choice\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024marks a decade since Cox was diagnosed with multiple sclerosis and the last year has been perhaps her roughest yet, racked with relapses and plagued with injuries.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 543}, {\"ngram\": \"Cox\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple sclerosis\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"the last year\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"her roughest\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 658}, {\"ngram\": \"relapses\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It all culminated in a cruel crash on the first turn of the 500m time trial, an event in which the 33-year-old was meant to win ParalympicsGB's first medal of the Games and retain her title.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cruel crash\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"the first turn\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 765}, {\"ngram\": \"the 500m time trial\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"ParalympicsGB's first medal\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"her title\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The fact that I got here was amazing in itself,\\\" said Cox, who posted the second-quickest time in qualifying.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fact\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"Cox\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"the second-quickest time\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifying\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just gutted that I was able to ride a ride that was pretty great in the first round and then not go out there and show what I am capable of.\\\"\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a ride\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cox only got back on the bike two weeks ago after a calf tear and was in a protective boot less than a month ago.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cox\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"a calf tear\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"a protective boot\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time last year, she could not walk after a serious relapse of MS affected her right side and it was weakness in that part of her body that proved her undoing in the final.\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1347, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Multiple_sclerosis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0495421442960878e-14, \"text\": \"MS\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Multiple_sclerosis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Multiple_sclerosis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a serious relapse\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"her right side\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"weakness\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"that part\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"her body\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world record holder looked strong in qualification but slipped out of the start gate at the start of the final.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The world record holder\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"qualification\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"the start gate\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the right side of her body impacted, she was unable to correct her course and veered violently onto the cote d'azur to crash on the first turn.\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right side\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"her body\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"her course\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"the cote d'azur\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"the first turn\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under UCI rules, only a mechanical issue could have seen her granted a restart and Dutch rider Caroline Groot was left to take the Briton's title.\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.888957587438253e-13, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}, {\"begin\": 1808, \"end\": 1813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.8161679527986939, \"rank\": 0.1856220121353675, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 1820, \"end\": 1834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Groot\", \"score\": 0.9999933051532396, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caroline Groot\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Groot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Groot\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only a mechanical issue\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"the Briton's title\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cox spent nearly 30 minutes lying on the floor of the track centre in floods of tears and took more than an hour to compose herself for an interview with Channel 4.\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cox\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 30 minutes\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1919}, {\"ngram\": \"the track centre\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"floods\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"more than an hour\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2021}, {\"ngram\": \"Channel\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a weird one, I did not feel comfortable in the gate,\\\" said Cox, who is one of over 1,000 elite athletes on UK Sport's National Lottery-funded World Class Programme, allowing them to train full time, have access to the world's best coaches and benefit from pioneering medical support - which has been vital on their pathway to the Paris 2024 Games.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2154, \"end\": 2162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 2154, \"end\": 2162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a weird one\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"the gate\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"Cox\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"over 1,000 elite athletes\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best coaches\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2285}, {\"ngram\": \"medical support\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"their pathway\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2369}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Games\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With a condition like mine, riding can not always be perfect, and it was all over the shop.\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a condition\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"mine\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"riding\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2431}, {\"ngram\": \"the shop\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been a rollercoaster, I guess that's MS.\\\" Cox first pierced the public consciousness at Rio 2016, where she became the first British athlete in 32 years to win medals in multiple sports across athletics and cycling.\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2622, \"end\": 2629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9878770588349256, \"rank\": 0.011169297306509198, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rollercoaster\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"MS\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2535}, {\"ngram\": \"Cox\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"the public consciousness\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2580}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio 2016\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2592}, {\"ngram\": \"32 years\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple sports\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2681}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In doing so she inspired Daphne Schrager to swap the track for the velodrome and now the 23-year-old has a silver medal to her name, ParalympicsGB's first of the Games.\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2739, \"end\": 2745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daphne_Blake\", \"score\": 0.9999962644184703, \"rank\": 3.7355956801264348e-06, \"text\": \"Daphne\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daphne_Blake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daphne_Blake\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2772}, {\"ngram\": \"the velodrome\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2790}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2833}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schrager started out as a 100m sprinter and competed in athletics at the 2018 Commonwealth Games but having fallen out of love with the sport, she switched to cycling having never ridden before.\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 3078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schrager\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2892}, {\"ngram\": \"a 100m sprinter\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2018 Commonwealth Games\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3010}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schrager's silver was presented to her by the actor Jackie Chan, a special ambassador for the International Paralympic Committee.\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3131, \"end\": 3142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Chan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9117478251014235e-33, \"text\": \"Jackie Chan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Chan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Chan\"}, {\"begin\": 3173, \"end\": 3207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Paralympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schrager's silver\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3096}, {\"ngram\": \"a special ambassador\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't even allowed to ride a bike as a kid,\\\" said Schrager, who has cerebral palsy.\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bike\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3247}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3256}, {\"ngram\": \"Schrager\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3272}, {\"ngram\": \"cerebral palsy\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They thought I'd just fall off and plough into a tree.\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tree\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have started from scratch, and it has been a right journey.\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"scratch\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"a right journey\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The improvement I have made on the programme has been amazing and I am so lucky to be one of the people on National Lottery funding.\\\"\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3525, \"end\": 3549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Community_Fund\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Lottery funding\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Community_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Community_Fund\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The improvement\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3433}, {\"ngram\": \"the programme\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3462}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schrager was devastated to see her idol Cox crash out, with the Leeds native hoping to be back for the mixed relay event.\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schrager\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3561}, {\"ngram\": \"her idol\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3592}, {\"ngram\": \"Cox\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3596}, {\"ngram\": \"the Leeds native\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3629}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed relay event\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Kadeena was the one that got me into this,\\\" said Schrager.\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kadeena\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3684}, {\"ngram\": \"the one\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3696}, {\"ngram\": \"Schrager\", \"from\": 3726, \"to\": 3734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's a great human so she will be back, we will pick her up as a team and she will come and prove what she's worth.\\\"\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great human\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3756}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cox added: \\\"The boys are going to be counting on me to go out and deliver a quick lap so I am hoping I can get my head back in the game and go out there for them.\", \"from\": 3856, \"to\": 4018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cox\", \"from\": 3856, \"to\": 3859}, {\"ngram\": \"The boys\", \"from\": 3868, \"to\": 3876}, {\"ngram\": \"a quick lap\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 3941}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 3967, \"to\": 3974}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 3991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been a rough week; I have been struggling with my mental health, so I really need to go out and speak to my psychologist and just get my head back in gear.\\\"\", \"from\": 4019, \"to\": 4182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rough week\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4043}, {\"ngram\": \"my mental health\", \"from\": 4073, \"to\": 4089}, {\"ngram\": \"my psychologist\", \"from\": 4131, \"to\": 4146}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 4160, \"to\": 4167}, {\"ngram\": \"gear\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"::With more than \\u00a330M a week raised for Good Causes, including vital funding into elite and grassroots sport, National Lottery players support our Olympic and Paralympic athletes to live their dreams and make the nation proud, as well as providing more opportunities for people to take part in sport.\", \"from\": 4184, \"to\": 4484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4294, \"end\": 4310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"score\": 0.9999999999772626, \"rank\": 2.2569943839994867e-11, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than \\u00a330M\", \"from\": 4191, \"to\": 4205}, {\"ngram\": \"Good Causes\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4235}, {\"ngram\": \"vita